text:
Mikael Jansson, George Cortina & Jason Gay Gisele Bündchen Is a Force of Nature
Writer Jason Gay (bottom right) was scheduled to interview supermodel Gisele Bündchen days before her husband, Tom Brady, quarterbacked the New England Patriots in the Super Bowl. Gay was concerned that Bündchen would be distracted. “Turns out [the Brady-Bündchen household] was a pretty chill scene. Going to a Super Bowl is pretty routine for Gisele,” Gay says. Mikael Jansson (left) photographed Bündchen with styling by George Cortina (top right) in Brookhaven, New York—a Long Island town boasting woods, grasslands and saltwater wetlands...
